So it got pretty heated!!!!! Anyway the pitcher is okay-and we sent them packing to the loser's bracket.  But I  thought this guy crossed the line and the umps should have tossed him but did nothing!!!!  Maybe  next time he will pitch and we'll see how he likes it or maybe he should stay home and clip his toe nails!!<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rollin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/roll.gif ALT=":rollin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/boklahomasoftball.showUserPublicProfile?gid=biggurl1st@oklahomasoftball>biggurl1st</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 18<br> <font color=#8B0000>(7/29/03 10:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=464.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: A short story about the boy they call &quot;toe nail&quo</span><hr size=1> SORRY TO HEAR ABOUT YOUR PITCHER, BUT IT IS KINDA A FUNNY STORY.  SOUNDS LIKE HE IS JUST A BIG PUSS! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=464.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=464.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=464.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/baseball/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/foklahomasoftballfrm2.emailToFrie